      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-h2 mb-4">추천 금융상품</h2>
        <div class="border-b border-kb-border-gray">
          <nav class="-mb-px flex space-x-6 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar" aria-label="Tabs">
            <a href="#" class="tab-item tab-item-active">전체</a>
            <a href="#" class="tab-item">예금/적금</a>
            <a href="#" class="tab-item">펀드</a>
            <a href="#" class="tab-item">대출</a>
            <a href="#" class="tab-item">카드</a>
            <a href="#" class="tab-item">외환</a>
          </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 scroll-container no-scrollbar">
          <div class="card-interactive shrink-0 w-72">
            <span class="badge badge-deposit">예금</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">KB Star 정기예금</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1 h-10">내손으로 만드는 DIY포트폴리오 예금</p>
            <div class="text-right mt-4"><a href="#" class="btn-text">자세히 보기 &gt;</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-interactive shrink-0 w-72">
            <span class="badge badge-fund">펀드</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">KB 코리아밸류 펀드</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1 h-10">대한민국 가치주에 투자하는 대표 펀드입니다.</p>
            <div class="text-right mt-4"><a href="#" class="btn-text">자세히 보기 &gt;</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-interactive shrink-0 w-72">
            <span class="badge badge-loan">대출</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">KB 직장인든든 신용대출</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1 h-10">복잡한 서류 없이 빠르게! 직장인을 위한 든든한 대출</p>
            <div class="text-right mt-4"><a href="#" class="btn-text">자세히 보기 &gt;</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-interactive shrink-0 w-72">
            <span class="badge badge-exchange">외환</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">KB 국민 첫 외화예금</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1 h-10">환율우대와 수수료 혜택을 동시에 누리세요.</p>
            <div class="text-right mt-4"><a href="#" class="btn-text">자세히 보기 &gt;</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-h2 mb-6">이벤트/소식</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="card-base">
            <span class="badge badge-yellow">인기 이벤트</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">KB와 함께하는 여름 페스티벌</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1">이벤트 참여하고 시원한 경품 받아가세요! (~8/31)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-base">
            <span class="badge badge-blue">NEW</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">신규 서비스 오픈 안내</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1">마이데이터 서비스가 새롭게 오픈되었습니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-base">
            <span class="badge badge-gray">공지</span>
            <h3 class="text-title-h3 mt-3">시스템 정기 점검 안내</h3>
            <p class="text-caption mt-1">9월 15일(일) 00:00 ~ 04:00. 서비스 이용이 제한됩니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-h2 mb-6">가입 및 신청 양식 예제</h2>
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="form-label">이름</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="name"
                class="form-input"
                placeholder="실명을 입력하세요"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="form-label">휴대폰 번호</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="phone"
                class="form-input"
                placeholder="'-' 없이 숫자만 입력"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="form-label">약관 동의</span>
              <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
                <div class="form-control-group">
                  <input id="agree-all" type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox" />
                  <label for="agree-all">전체 동의</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-control-group ml-4">
                  <input id="agree-1" type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox" />
                  <label for="agree-1">서비스 이용약관 동의 (필수)</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-control-group ml-4">
                  <input id="agree-2" type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox" />
                  <label for="agree-2">개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의 (필수)</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="form-label">마케팅 정보 수신</span>
              <div class="mt-2 flex space-x-6">
                <div class="form-control-group">
                  <input
                    id="marketing-yes"
                    name="marketing"
                    type="radio"
                    class="form-radio"
                    checked
                  />
                  <label for="marketing-yes">동의함</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-control-group">
                  <input id="marketing-no" name="marketing" type="radio" class="form-radio" />
                  <label for="marketing-no">동의안함</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-h2 mb-6">거래 내역 조회</h2>
        <div class="table-wrapper">
          <table class="table-kb">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>거래일시</th>
                <th>적요</th>
                <th>입금액</th>
                <th>출금액</th>
                <th>거래후 잔액</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>2025.09.05 14:30</td>
                <td>이자</td>
                <td class="text-blue-600">5,120원</td>
                <td>-</td>
                <td>1,005,120원</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>2025.09.04 11:15</td>
                <td>KB카드출금</td>
                <td>-</td>
                <td class="text-red-600">150,000원</td>
                <td>1,000,000원</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>2025.09.01 09:00</td>
                <td>급여</td>
                <td class="text-blue-600">2,500,000원</td>
                <td>-</td>
                <td>1,150,000원</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <nav class="mt-6">
          <div class="pagination">
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item pagination-item-disabled">&lt;</a>
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item pagination-item-active">1</a>
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item">2</a>
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item">3</a>
            <span class="pagination-item">...</span>
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item">10</a>
            <a href="#" class="pagination-item">&gt;</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-h2 mb-6">알림 메시지 예제</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="alert alert-success">
            <svg
              class="alert-icon"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <strong>성공:</strong>
            이체가 정상적으로 완료되었습니다.
          </div>
          <div class="alert alert-warning">
            <svg
              class="alert-icon"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
